{"tid":453431,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"著曼聯衫睇印尼大戰 球迷被包圍強脫球衣 推落看台致骨折","createTime":"2017-10-31T07:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T05:07:29.000Z","uid":9030,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b8142bb286a8008ad301bcdf81e783b4346efd0c","tid":453431,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"轉自cjc巴打:<br />\n<br />\n【著曼聯衫睇印尼大戰好危險】<br />\n<br />\n11月3日星期五中午將會舉行印尼聯賽老打吡，今次由Persija主場對Persib，即係佩斯查對佩斯比，又即係雅加達對萬隆，世界上最火爆嘅打吡大戰之一。<br />\n<br />\n不過同以往唔同，今次安排喺星期五中午踢而唔係禮拜六日，而且比賽安排喺中爪哇省梭羅市舉行，由雅加達前往當地要10粒鐘車程。<br />\n<br />\n有咁嘅安排係賽會故意，因為上輪萬隆主場時有萬隆球迷懷疑比對家球迷打死，呢兩派球迷關係從來唔好，多年來衝突造成好多球迷死傷，為免再新增亡魂，比賽移師去中立場舉行。<br />\n<br />\n但根據過往紀錄，即使係工作天日頭踢都可以有萬幾二萬人入場，因為比賽有一定吸引性，有唔少球迷願意放低工作學業坐10粒鐘車去現場聲援球隊，其實暴力事件好難冇，只係冇喺雅加達踢咁危險啫，就算閉門，球迷照樣可以喺出面打交生事。<br />\n<br />\n上年佩斯查主場對萬隆都係喺中立場踢，嗰陣原因係佩斯查冇主場可用而暫時以梭羅市作為基地，不過都有接近3萬人入場，差唔多爆滿。<br />\n<br />\n氣氛雖然刺熱，但場內暴力場面好多，包括一名身穿曼聯球衣嘅肥仔，佢非常慘，畀人打嘅原因，就係因為有人自稱討厭曼聯，最後肥仔比軍人救出，但波衫已經比人撕成碎片。"},{"pid":"190a7cafc4240fa10f94b9d621d6106f7e0d3c7e","tid":453431,"uid":785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:35:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">但波衫已經比人撕成碎片</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52107e8a9d2c57e26dc4af08b2577fa38d12ecd","tid":453431,"uid":9030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/sESp9k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FsESp9k.jpg&h=feefafee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/Jr9bn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FJr9bn6.jpg&h=5782c263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/kBULp3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FkBULp3.jpg&h=0afbc60c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i/fnK9bH.jpg[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FfnK9bH.jpg%5Bimg%5D&d=buFYMUadxM7cOVM0KOViTC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d9ad56c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i/fnK9bH.jpg[img]</a>"},{"pid":"672fd5284e230100f71c92431dc69697573278f5","tid":453431,"uid":19126,"like":37,"dislike":5,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:37:33.000Z","msg":"睇波睇到生蕃咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a142c33983defca92d5f6732641008dffd9872","tid":453431,"uid":33206,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:39:34.000Z","msg":"我唔睇波，真係唔明點解球迷可以咁唔文明"},{"pid":"06a194434da8e1fc775cdcde9e2c9dc5d1c2e7b1","tid":453431,"uid":19126,"like":24,"dislike":7,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔睇波，真係唔明點解球迷可以咁唔文明</blockquote><br />\n睇地區架姐，亞洲波不嬲低質架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b461b50e649c2e207844e815a0159f70cbd5e288","tid":453431,"uid":139252,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"印尼 不意外"},{"pid":"3777db9bac4f7eaae010f1f737b00bd2cc6468ea","tid":453431,"uid":65298,"like":64,"dislike":8,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印尼 不意外</blockquote><br />\n曼聯 不意外"},{"pid":"81a1443e024bc2a872308776a11e968363a96323","tid":453431,"uid":63423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:47:20.000Z","msg":"同隊波友都打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0459bfd40e87867a420a253e50b5550e6daa6423","tid":453431,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:47:21.000Z","msg":"個屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戀愛了"},{"pid"