撚就無鳩用啦<br />\n又唔打鳩佢地</blockquote><br />\n岩呀利狗正垃圾"},{"pid":"8fb575c7f27c669c8d452afbe9c4610e97895f13","tid":453431,"uid":37735,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我唔睇波，真係唔明點解球迷可以咁唔文明</blockquote><br />\n睇地區架姐，亞洲波不嬲低質架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英國 歐洲打得仲勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e303eb4ab5dff82013a9a84b506234e1be4ca51c","tid":453431,"uid":124667,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喂上次好多人話唔係利物浦主場<br />\n著曼聯衫去睇英超挑戰賽冇問題<br />\n希望果班傻閪俾人打撚死就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁班香港猁撚就無鳩用啦<br />\n又唔打鳩佢地</blockquote><br />\n岩呀利狗正垃圾</blockquote><br />\n下次打番囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1e85273436497555064d44dac3ad7d58160167","tid":453431,"uid":45487,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:22:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/259900/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/259900/page/1</a><br />\n要數倫敦死敵，當然還有今屆一直將熱刺壓在身後的車路士。藍戰士的球衣在大球場特別顯眼，阿言指今季一直提心吊膽害怕被熱刺追上，但今場不撐熱刺不撐傑志，「<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入場是撐車路士，告訴熱刺誰是英超冠軍</span></span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n藍戰士並不獨行，阿言透露在路上看見很多車路士球迷，說罷隨即有三名藍軍球迷路過。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/604160/xlarge/c0b47101490cc535ed4dc5e006e2d80a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F604160%2Fxlarge%2Fc0b47101490cc535ed4dc5e006e2d80a.jpg&h=005a67fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/604170/xlarge/b086409a71538f787344188ea70d73a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F604170%2Fxlarge%2Fb086409a71538f787344